{"tid":671202,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"琴日人生第一次去 i.t ( 好似係 )買野","createTime":"2018-05-20T02:54:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-20T16:26:18.000Z","uid":17275,"like":4,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9d6024e2a3d9898bb0e2e718020620a8e5d73ceb","tid":671202,"uid":17275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T02:54:00.000Z","msg":"話說平時都唔係好敢買衫褲.. <br />\n一條褲同一件衫可以著足2 星期( U RIGHT未汁之前買 )其實外型唔太毒..識著的話 <br />\n但因為讀左POLY 呢D 潮童學校..見D人個個都著得好潮咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我再著完本果D衫就會比人排斥..(雖然而經排緊) <br />\n所以諗住打聽下佢地響邊到買D衫返黎著(由於我朋友唔多..所以揀左偷聽) <br />\n我上星期聽到有2 個男仔講緊買衫果D野 ..話咩做SALE..所以決定跟住佢地諗住打聽下佢地邊到買衫.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但一聽之下聽到 咩 I.T！??...我開頭以為揀錯人...搵左2 個讀 IT GE毒撚 <br />\n點知我響高登都見過人講呢個字..所以上網search <br />\n<br />\nsearch完之後知道旺角有 it..所以專登早d去..點知成 8 點幾都未開門.... <br />\n<br />\n我響等門口等左 3 個鍾到...終於開門 <br />\n我響門口企左成20分鐘都唔敢入..d sales 眼望望咁...之後我衝左入廁所 <br />\n面住個馬桶係咁講粗口...又諗下軍曹點樣支持我...之後就諗住用跑ge方法進入 I.T <br />\n入到去D SALES係咁同我講野 <br />\n我由中2 果年開始就冇再同女仔講過野(咁又誇張左D..以前我同小食部個啊姐幾熟) <br />\n有個女SALES (高我6/3個頭到)係咁叫我買條褲 <br />\n我話我咩都唔識..我問佢洗唔洗比左錢先有得試身 <br />\n之後佢好有禮貌咁話唔洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n我果刻好開心..開心GE唔係唔洗比錢..而係我成功同到女仔講野 <br />\n我就咁入左試身室...其實我冇試到條褲..企左2分鐘到 <br />\n就出去比錢 <br />\n我拎上年新年D利士黎比...但帶出黎之前唔記得左開封利士 <br />\n之後係個SALES 面前開..佢唔知點解笑左一笑.. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n之後我就好驚咁話唔洗找..之後係咁跑出間I.T<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e0bf6309050569f40455f867fbf6c95717d3ac","tid":671202,"uid":17275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T03:07:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a47f270498cce38cab131497777c0b60244f91","tid":671202,"uid":17275,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"由於我12點到就買到條褲....諗住晏就有堂可以即刻show比d同學睇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我驚d同學好大鄉理唔知我條褲響邊到買... <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以我條褲冇剪到牌就著上身..比人睇我條褲響i.t買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (其實呢種自豪心理係人都有) <br />\n但我又驚同學人笑我著得唔好睇..所以我原本條褲冇除仲著響裡面 <br />\n等d同學一笑我就跑入廁所除左佢,當冇事發生過 <br />\n<br />\n我一返到學校...我得到前所未有ge滿足 <br />\nd女同學係咁望住我..(我覺我自己有小小似周拍豪) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢地一同我有眼神接觸時..我就單一單眼示意佢地望望我條褲個牌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等佢地知道我條褲響it到買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7fe9cd6bb1ffcb26db335546c2a23ae8f5fe099","tid":671202,"uid":57941,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T03:31:21.000Z","msg":"做咩姐你"},{"pid":"747626ba8b438bdccdf4205a4c38ea8754d18693","tid":671202,"uid":33174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T05:54:59.000Z","msg":"繼續打 想學下襯衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依家都係著baleno 想學下樓主做潮人"},{"pid":"bcb514f2a5058a6c2fdf473b031019c1b4bea163","tid":671202,"uid":4431,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T06:23:16.000Z","msg":"Bossini 系毒撚跪求潮童襯衫教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb914bf6edb7231e9b76f755ded5edc56c0b053a","tid":671202,"uid":113546,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T15:54:16.000Z","msg":"菊花牌小背心求教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5662b80364ca4b4e79a7ed7c99f967f187e1ff3e","tid":671202,"uid":106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:20:09.000Z","msg":"樓主我都著緊giordano<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 教下我去it (係咪咁串?) 買野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3163f11c4f80b4be5c5a50ad0c59d50d4dadb061","tid":671202,"uid":42402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-20T16:26:18.000Z","msg":"作啲新野嚟睇下好冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}